video.title: Mar de plástico
video.synopsis: In a town in southern Spain where racial tensions run high among the workers in its many greenhouses, a cop investigates the murder of a young woman.

episodes.synopsis: Ainhoa falls victim to a crime in the greenhouses of Campoamargo. Héctor, the new sergeant, discovers compromising information.
episodes.title: Las Primeras 48 Horas

episodes.synopsis: Marta suffers an accident after activating the fumigation system in the greenhouses. Lucas is detained for having threatened Ainhoa.
episodes.title: Fumigación

episodes.synopsis: The neighbors of Campoamargo receive a message about Ainhoa. Lola and Héctor find a suspicious burned vehicle. Lucas is chased.
episodes.title: Reconstrucción

episodes.synopsis: Héctor asks to analyze a sample from the crime scene. Fara suffers a terrifyingly similar experience. Marta confesses something to Héctor.
episodes.title: La Prueba

episodes.synopsis: Someone who was spying on Mar also filmed Ainhoa mere hours before her murder. Salva discovers new information on Agneska’s lover.
episodes.title: La Cámara

episodes.synopsis: Héctor is closing in on clues that will uncover Ainhoa’s murderer. The only witness to the mayor’s daughter’s last moments begins to draw blanks.
episodes.title: Confianza

episodes.synopsis: The coroner rules the latest death a suicide. Héctor isn’t so sure and decides to investigate. Marta discovers secrets about her husband’s death.
episodes.title: La Mano

episodes.synopsis: New evidence about Ainhoa’s murder that may implicate Juan Rueda surfaces. The second lieutenant offers another version of the story to the police.
episodes.title: El Pasado

episodes.synopsis: The death of a foreign girl twenty years ago may be related to Ainhoa’s death. Héctor flat out rejects this notion.
episodes.title: La Fosa

episodes.synopsis: Juan Rueda is detained after a grave is found on his property, but he can’t be charged. The investigation seems to have hit a dead end.
episodes.title: Fuera de Combate

episodes.synopsis: DNA evidence is found on Ainhoa’s body and Juan Rueda is detained once again. Héctor urges the judge for more time to investigate the findings.
episodes.title: Boris.E

episodes.synopsis: Héctor and his team have another theory about Ainhoa’s murderer’s true identity. Questions about the Romanian child begin to arise.
episodes.title: Se Cierra el Círculo

episodes.synopsis: Lola, Salva, and Héctor continue their investigation into the elusive Boris. They begin by looking into the pistol used to shoot the sergeant.
episodes.title: La Caza del Hombre

episodes.synopsis: Salva finds Marta’s body and fear once again spreads throughout Campoamargo.
episodes.title: El Regreso

episodes.synopsis: As was the case with Marta's death, the discovery of Barislav’s body yields no DNA evidence. But clues are later found at Barislav’s house.
episodes.title: Barislav 4

episodes.synopsis: Pablo confronts Héctor over photos linked to the murder. Héctor submits to a polygraph test.
episodes.title: Cowboy De Medianoche

episodes.synopsis: Héctor searches Francisco’s phone. Fernando has a face to face meeting with Cristina in prison. Investigators discover letters belonging to Fernando.
episodes.title: La Trituradora

episodes.synopsis: Héctor studies the anonymous clues that Fernando received. Sergio finds Agneska and Pablo together.
episodes.title: Quid Pro Quo

episodes.synopsis: Kaled finds a bloodied youngster on the highway. Héctor finds out that she has an interesting tattoo. The girl manages to utter a name: Vlad.
episodes.title: Pit Bull

episodes.synopsis: Lola and Salva arrive in prison and search for a book with mysterious letters but end up finding nothing. Héctor receives new information.
episodes.title: Vlad

episodes.synopsis: Guineans and Roma encounter each other after mass. Sergio goes to see his brother in prison. Sergio makes mention of an interesting blog.
episodes.title: El Día De La Ira

episodes.synopsis: A woman accuses Pilar of having imprisoned her. Vlad faces off against the head of the gang. A big secret is finally revealed.
episodes.title: Marta

episodes.synopsis: The investigators see the photos and look at the silhouette of what looks like a bike. The investigators identify the model.
episodes.title: Yo Confieso

episodes.synopsis: Vlad informs the investigators that he has exculpatory evidence in his house. Fernando is threatened in prison.
episodes.title: Cazado

episodes.synopsis: Héctor investigates and discovers that Cristina was abused by her father when she was young. The police find a notebook full of numbers and charts.
episodes.title: Cristina

episodes.synopsis: Rueda barely survives. Lola, Héctor, and Salva arrive and find the murderer. They later manage to uncover the killer's identity.
episodes.title: ¿Quién Mató A Marta?
